# enumeratedNumbers

**Instance Property**

A set of the numbers allowed in this constraint.

## Declaration

```swift
var enumeratedNumbers: Set<NSNumber>? { get }
```

## Numeric Constraints

- **minNumber**: The smallest numerical value allowed by this constraint.
- **maxNumber**: The largest numerical value allowed by this constraint.
